Not bundled (you fetch these separately)
----------------------------------------
* ST7305_U8g2.h / ST7305_U8g2.cpp — the ST7305 reflective-LCD driver for this board.
    Source: Waveshare ESP32-S3-RLCD-4.2 demo, 02_Example/Arduino/10_U8G2_Test/
    https://github.com/waveshareteam/ESP32-S3-RLCD-4.2
    Copy these into firmware/claude_slate/ before building. They are Waveshare's
    code and are deliberately NOT redistributed in this repository.
* U8g2 (patched build with u8x8_d_st7305) — ships in the same Waveshare repo under
    01_Arduino_Libraries/U8g2. Upstream U8g2 is by Oliver Kraus (BSD-2-Clause):
    https://github.com/olikraus/u8g2

